Oh yes, she died at home, died - she had - oh we moved down to the Toll House then and - there was a set - two sitting rooms, she was in there the latter part of the time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6762071 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10314666\charrsid8475667 Did your father go to church too?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16153212 MR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10314666\charrsid8475667 
Oh yes, yes, he - but he hadn't been confirmed, he was confirmed - - when he was older, oh yes my father always went to church, he was a very good living man.
