{\*\xmlclose}
 and it is inclined to be cold. Washing, and also go out and do a little cleaning. But only - but - but - you know, I - not - not a lot. Well you see money was very short those days. 'Cos the most my father was ever able - able - to give me to keep house
 was twelve shillings a week, and you see - when they are - both retired - I had - they only had ten - on - when me father retired at - suppose it was the beginning of the - well during the war he was old - he - I had ten shillings a week pension, well of
