master lost his wife - married again and she had - they had an evening class and I used to go and do }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6973851\charrsid8475667 needlework}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
