He did that. Then he went in for another examination with a large drawing of t
he egg plant. You know what I mean? And he passed, he could really - could have taught drawing if he liked. And then he was a gardener, he went under gardener different places and - he was gard - gard - head gardener to Lord Dceces when war broke out and 
