e said if you join the army you won't come back here no more. But he had an ac - he - got a very deformed arm, he had an accident in the field, and he did that so as he got in, of course they were anxious for recruits then and he passed and - all the hort
icultural he was very good at learning, and Edward the younger brother got some nice peaches which he drew - with a pencil.
