\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16153212 MR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10314666\charrsid8475667 Well -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6762071 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10314666\charrsid8475667 The war was still on when you moved in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16153212 MR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10314666\charrsid8475667 
No, I think it was ended. Yes, it was ended because we got rid of the soldiers and that. What I told you about them yet. And - and we'd had - it used to be - a little shop and the grammar school boy
s and the boys - the old - the old lady what lived there about ninety-six when she died, the old mother-in-law, the son came down with consumption and died, the mother-in-law - lived there 'til she was about ninety-six and then the daughter-in-law, she wa
s
 a spiteful woman. But there was four steps down into the back kitchen which was very trying, I - and - well then after my brother got it'll you see they run this business and the other one up Wickham Road retired and he was on his own and - he got ill an
d
 had to go hospital and have his lung removed. And - he never got better, he couldn't do no work and he - he got very hard up 'cos I'd only got ten shillings a week pension, he had his stick pay, and - I asked the council if they could find him - one of t
hese prefabs 'cos his breath was bad you see, and she couldn't sell the business, the blacksmiths was dying out, he - and he had a lot of debts, never got his money, and so they give us this house. So patient, I never heard him complain.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6762071 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10314666\charrsid8475667 Did you get on well with him when you were children too?
