Yes, that was six weeks, I don't think the farmers would be bothered with you. They didn't take many young men you see becau
se - I mean - they didn't retire at sixty-five 'cos my father was - over seventy when he left off work, and then he just couldn't get up in the mornings that's what made us without a home you see. But of course the house goes with the job. It does now you
 know. It does still. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6762071 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10314666\charrsid8475667 
But those families that weren't too clean, did you - you could play with those children if you wanted to could you?
