Well no she didn't like me to go with dirty children. No, 'cos you see she'd got all of us, and Every Saturday night they - they had a wooden tub to do the washing with a little }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6773215\charrsid8475667 piece}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10314666\charrsid8475667 
 of wood in the corner for the soap and every Saturday night - in - in the front of the fire we all had a good bath. Oh every one, every Saturday night.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6762071 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10314666\charrsid8475667 It must have been a lot of work that heating the water?
