e, when - after a time she lost her sight, never. No, she worked hard. As I tell you she went out washing one day - she used to go once a month and do the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6773215\charrsid8475667 
farmers}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10314666\charrsid8475667  washing. Once a month. Oh yes, you had to work then.
