Oh yes, yes, as I tell you my father I think he was in being a soldier was a - was - I - I got his }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6773215\charrsid8475667 pay book}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
