No, we never had any beer. Nor didn't my father and that. He never went - he used to go once a quarter to his pay his club but he never had beer. Oh -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6762071 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10314666\charrsid8475667 He didn't go to the pub?
