No, not - not - I can't remember - mother used to say we ought to but of course you know what - those big boys they got big but they weren't too bad. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6762071 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10314666\charrsid8475667 Were you taught to say prayers at night?
