or's granddaughter now and she - and she - oh - nowadays - money means more to people than it used to. Do you see my meaning? 'Cos you couldn't possibly pay your neighbours and that for it. And that, and - I don't know, although I find a lot of kindness, 
even among young people. And I dislike - hearing all this about what - these people do, that's only the minority of 'em.
