i
th all we children if we didn't obey her? I mean she couldn't have done any - any the more I think of her the more amazed I am at the self-sacrifice her whole life was. Even after she went blind she done a lot for us and - she used to make and things, bec
ause - they want - asked me if I wanted to learn to make anything but my fingers don't feel like hers did you see. And I can't be worried. And -
