Well I went in Saffron Waldon hospital, I was there three years. I was matron's maid. And then I went in - into the laundry. I got nine pound a year when I was matron's maid, paid quarterly. And go -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6762071 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10314666\charrsid8475667 What did you do with the money?
