ng older but I can - continually in the Girls Friendly Society and was made a member, and we had a - a class every week, a - a - Bible - }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6773215\charrsid8475667 the vicars}{\rtlch\fcs1 
