inging and we had - we sung - {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname PlaceType}}Land{\*\xmlclose} of {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname PlaceName}}Hope{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}
