Yes. I - I never connected the tradesmen with - well there wasn't many - well there was harness maker, butcher and the - a drapers we had then which we haven't got a drapers shop, we've got those four antiques and another one coming.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6762071 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10314666\charrsid8475667 So where would you place the tradesmen?
