earn me anything else, that was before any rules or regulations come in, there was nobody to come round to see if you went to school 'til long after I left.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6762071 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10314666\charrsid8475667 You didn't have a labour certificate?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16153212 MR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10314666\charrsid8475667 No, was no - that was just a school, it wasn't eve
n a board school then. And when this older sister went to school first mother had to pay tuppence a week. But she didn't pay that - she's eight years older than me, and - nothing was paid, but you see I went, there was only two classrooms and just a littl
e fire in the wall. And - when I got into the big room as we called it I was in standard five and - I couldn't - learn any more, so I just left and got a little job as a day girl. One and six a week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6762071 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10314666\charrsid8475667 That was before you went away to be with the hospital?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16153212 MR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10314666\charrsid8475667 
Oh yes, yes, 'cos I had another day girl job after that - a little better pay, well it wasn't much pay but it - I was older you see. But I used to - even before that I used to go - there were some people opposite, I used to go over and help - the 
- lady - do a little jobs and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6762071 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10314666\charrsid8475667 While you were still at school?
