d was the army Medical Crops and they came there to train ready to go - they went out to the desert. And I had letters from 'em and they - two of 'em came to see me one from Waltham Abbey just a few years ago.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6762071 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10314666\charrsid8475667 How long had he stayed with you then in the house?
