On - on - on dishes, she never served a meal to my knowledge out of the saucepans, and we all had - and I used to have to sit and behave ourself, well all had to behave at-
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6762071 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10314666\charrsid8475667 Was she particular about how you sat at the table?
