Well all had a high chair, and it went from my sister Meggie to - to - the youngest We all had the same high chair. My mother was very careful, never destroyed things you know. No, all had the same high chair.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6762071 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10314666\charrsid8475667 Can you reme
mber when you were a child if you were brought up to hit back if another child hit you, or didn't that happen?
