Well we kept quiet you see, we had little - things to play with, I had a little dooden doll. And you see really - there wasn't a lot of people, I had some aunts but you see - mother was busy all day and - 'cos she always had t
he toddlers you see to see after and look after and then you see we went to bed at night, always regularly in bed at seven o'clock in - or before in the winter and eight o'clock in the summer. Mm.
