Never, I never heard my father swear. He was a very quiet man. Never - I can truthfully sit here and tell you I never heard him in my life, and it was - never heard in our house.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6762071 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10314666\charrsid8475667 
