Oh they - well I couldn't say. But we had a - we had a little place here, we had a Salvation Army in Newport when I was young. Yes.
 Yes. And after we used to come out of Sunday school - and church on Sunday afternoons we used to go down there but we never dare let the parson know. And we used to love the singing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6762071 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10314666\charrsid8475667 You joined in did you?
