 an understood thing. 'Cos you see I believe - most of the farmers was Conservatives, but that wasn't why my - we vote - my father voted because he was always that way.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6762071 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10314666\charrsid8475667 He was convinced of it you mean?
