 mind you he was a good master, this Mr Shirley, Mr Brown has mentioned him - last week, I can remember how he would have been thirty years a church warden, he was a very respected man. He had no family but he brought up two nieces. And then - then.

\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6762071 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10314666\charrsid8475667 He was a respected men?
