\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16153212 MR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10314666\charrsid8475667 
Well no, they used to go there and play and that, they - they had a daughter, Elsie Myer and she - she hired - the mother hired this house - 'cos her father died, the war -
 upset him so, he was a German banker or something and - I think money was involved and - and she hired this house and - she had a - a person down there to - cook, a Miss Petty, and they used to have penny dinners.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6762071 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10314666\charrsid8475667 Was that in the second war?
