No, children, they called her Miss Petty, she used to speak on - she - afterwards when she went away she spoke on the wireless and she - and -
 Elsie Myer, the daughter used to come and play with the children and go up to - to the - well it was a board school then, they call it primary, and play with the children once a week. They were very nice, mm.
