Oh yes, we used to have a magic lantern sometimes. And - one - every now and then there used to be a party 
of players come and - and - in the village hall and they used to do a play every night, lodge in the house - in the village for about a week, now and again.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6762071 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10314666\charrsid8475667 Can you remember any of the plays they did?
