\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6762071 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10314666\charrsid8475667 She'd seen that had she?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16153212 MR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10314666\charrsid8475667 
Well I don't know whether she'd seen it, she'd read about it. Mm. And then of cou
rse we had the Moat Farm murder near here, and they used to bring Dougal - to the Newport station - every week to - village hall to police court and - hundreds and hundreds of thousands of people went over to the Moat Farm, that's about, I should think th
r
ee or four mile, I walked there one day, and I saw - they used to pluck pieces off of the hedges and - they were getting some bones out the moat then but they turned out to be - calves bones, but they found Miss Holland eventually, but for - months and mo
nths before that transpired there was people in the village - policemen or de}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6297802\charrsid8475667 tec}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10314666\charrsid8475667 tives disguised in the pubs and that trying to find out where Miss Holland was -
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6762071 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10314666\charrsid8475667 Where did they find her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16153212 MR  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10314666\charrsid8475667 Well they found her in the ditch in the finish you know at 
the Moat Farm. I went up the station to see him but I knew him very well because - he used to - come to the shop opposite where we lived every week and he used to take his horse and that to be should to my brother's.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid6762071 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid10314666\charrsid8475667 Did he murder her then?
